title: Pretty Mountain Views No Hauling Groceries Upstairs!
text:
Pretty Mountain Views No Hauling Groceries Upstairs! ad date: 10/10/2015 
Groceries Upstairs! 16755 Thompson Road, Brookings Spacious custom 3 bed/3 ba 2-story home featuring upstairs living areas. Amenities include vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace and open kitchen with island. Master bedroom/bath has tray ceiling, walk-in closet, jetted tub and separate shower. Guest bed and bath on lower level. Dumbwaiter in garage so no hauling groceries! Tiled covered patio and extra parking for boat/RV, etc. No. 15302497 $379,000 Karen Kennedy
